metadata.name: PAPC-Genesis #557
metadata.description: Punk Ape Pixel Club-Genesis (PAPC-G), represents the extension of the PAPC-OG collection and consists of 5,000 unique and collectable Punk themed Apes on the Ethereum blockchain. A hybrid collection of two of the most iconic projects in the NFT space. Harnessing the pixelated power of Crypto Punks forged with BAYC DNA, PAPC-G will bring a new breed of NFT. Driven by evolution.
